Name: The Northman
Star: Alexander Skarsgård, Anya Taylor-Joy, Willem Dafoe, Nicole Kidman
Summary: From acclaimed director Robert Eggers, The Northman is an epic revenge thriller that explores how far a Viking prince will go to seek justice for his murdered father.

Name: The King's Man
Star: Ralph Fiennes, Gemma Arterton, Rhys Ifans, Harris Dickinson
Summary: In the early years of the 20th century, the Kingsman agency is formed to stand against a cabal plotting a war to wipe out millions.

Name: Pushpa: The Rise - Part 1
Star: Allu Arjun, Fahadh Faasil, Rashmika Mandanna, Dhananjaya
Summary: Story of Pushpa Raj, a lorry driver in Seshachalam forests of South India, set in the backdrop of red sandalwood smuggling. Red Sandalwood is endemic to South-Eastern Ghats (mountain range) of India.

Name: Station Eleven
Star: Joe Pingue, Mackenzie Davis, Himesh Patel, Matilda Lawler
Summary: A post apocalyptic saga spanning multiple timelines, telling the stories of survivors of a devastating flu as they attempt to rebuild and reimagine the world anew while holding on to the best of what's been lost.

Name: Die Hard
Star: Bruce Willis, Alan Rickman, Bonnie Bedelia, Reginald VelJohnson
Summary: An NYPD officer tries to save his wife and several others taken hostage by German terrorists during a Christmas party at the Nakatomi Plaza in Los Angeles.

Name: Nightmare Alley
Star: Bradley Cooper, Cate Blanchett, Toni Collette, Willem Dafoe
Summary: An ambitious carny with a talent for manipulating people with a few well-chosen words hooks up with a female psychiatrist who is even more dangerous than he is.

Name: Daredevil
Star: Charlie Cox, Vincent D'Onofrio, Deborah Ann Woll, Elden Henson
Summary: A blind lawyer by day, vigilante by night. Matt Murdock fights the crime of New York as Daredevil.

Name: No Time to Die
Star: Daniel Craig, Ana de Armas, Rami Malek, Léa Seydoux
Summary: James Bond has left active service. His peace is short-lived when Felix Leiter, an old friend from the CIA, turns up asking for help, leading Bond onto the trail of a mysterious villain armed with dangerous new technology.

Name: The Last Duel
Star: Matt Damon, Adam Driver, Jodie Comer, Harriet Walter
Summary: King Charles VI declares that Knight Jean de Carrouges settle his dispute with his squire by challenging him to a duel.

Name: Money Heist
Star: Úrsula Corberó, Álvaro Morte, Itziar Ituño, Pedro Alonso
Summary: An unusual group of robbers attempt to carry out the most perfect robbery in Spanish history - stealing 2.4 billion euros from the Royal Mint of Spain.

Name: Yellowjackets
Star: Melanie Lynskey, Tawny Cypress, Ella Purnell, Sophie Nélisse
Summary: A wildly talented high school girl soccer team becomes the (un)lucky survivors of a plane crash deep in the Ontario wilderness.

Name: Venom: Let There Be Carnage
Star: Tom Hardy, Woody Harrelson, Michelle Williams, Naomie Harris
Summary: Eddie Brock attempts to reignite his career by interviewing serial killer Cletus Kasady, who becomes the host of the symbiote Carnage and escapes prison after a failed execution.

Name: Dexter
Star: Michael C. Hall, Jennifer Carpenter, David Zayas, James Remar
Summary: He's smart. He's lovable. He's Dexter Morgan, America's favorite serial killer, who spends his days solving crimes and nights committing them. Golden Globe winner Michael C. Hall stars in the hit SHOWTIME Original Series.

Name: The Tragedy of Macbeth
Star: Denzel Washington, Frances McDormand, Alex Hassell, Bertie Carvel
Summary: A Scottish lord becomes convinced by a trio of witches that he will become the next King of Scotland, and his ambitious wife supports him in his plans of seizing power.

Name: The Walking Dead
Star: Andrew Lincoln, Norman Reedus, Melissa McBride, Lauren Cohan
Summary: Sheriff Deputy Rick Grimes wakes up from a coma to learn the world is in ruins and must lead a group of survivors to stay alive.

Name: The Girl Before
Star: Gugu Mbatha-Raw, Ben Hardy, Jessica Plummer, David Oyelowo
Summary: Jane falls in love with an extraordinary minimalist house, but when she discovers that another damaged woman died in the same property three years earlier, she starts to wonder if her own story is just a rerun of the girl before.

Name: Mayor of Kingstown
Star: Jeremy Renner, Dianne Wiest, Hugh Dillon, Tobi Bamtefa
Summary: The McLusky family are power brokers tackling themes of systemic racism, corruption and inequality in Kingstown, Michigan, where the business of incarceration is the only thriving industry.

Name: Red Notice
Star: Dwayne Johnson, Ryan Reynolds, Gal Gadot, Ritu Arya
Summary: An Interpol agent tracks the world's most wanted art thief.

Name: Breaking Bad
Star: Bryan Cranston, Aaron Paul, Anna Gunn, Betsy Brandt
Summary: A high school chemistry teacher diagnosed with inoperable lung cancer turns to manufacturing and selling methamphetamine in order to secure his family's future.

Name: Mother/Android
Star: Chloë Grace Moretz, Algee Smith, Raúl Castillo, Linnea Gardner
Summary: In a post-apocalyptic world rocked by a violent android uprising, a young pregnant woman and her boyfriend desperately search for safety.

Name: Squid Game
Star: Lee Jung-jae, Park Hae-soo, Wi Ha-Joon, Jung Hoyeon
Summary: Hundreds of cash-strapped players accept a strange invitation to compete in children's games. Inside, a tempting prize awaits with deadly high stakes. A survival game that has a whopping 45.6 billion-won prize at stake.

Name: Supernatural
Star: Jared Padalecki, Jensen Ackles, Jim Beaver, Misha Collins
Summary: Two brothers follow their father's footsteps as hunters, fighting evil supernatural beings of many kinds, including monsters, demons and gods that roam the earth.

Name: NCIS
Star: Mark Harmon, David McCallum, Sean Murray, Pauley Perrette
Summary: The cases of the Naval Criminal Investigative Service's Washington, D.C. Major Case Response Team, led by Special Agent Leroy Jethro Gibbs.

Name: Scream
Star: Neve Campbell, Courteney Cox, David Arquette, Marley Shelton
Summary: Twenty-five years after the original series of murders in Woodsboro, a new killer emerges, and Sidney Prescott must return to uncover the truth.

Name: You
Star: Penn Badgley, Victoria Pedretti, Ambyr Childers, Elizabeth Lail
Summary: A dangerously charming, intensely obsessive young man goes to extreme measures to insert himself into the lives of those he is transfixed by.

Name: The Blacklist
Star: James Spader, Megan Boone, Diego Klattenhoff, Ryan Eggold
Summary: A new FBI profiler, Elizabeth Keen, has her entire life uprooted when a mysterious criminal, Raymond Reddington, who has eluded capture for decades, turns himself in and insists on speaking only to her.

Name: Gomorrah
Star: Salvatore Esposito, Marco D'Amore, Ivana Lotito, Cristiana Dell'Anna
Summary: Ciro disregards tradition in his attempt to become the next boss of his crime syndicate. The internal power struggle puts him and his entire family's life at risk.

Name: Wrath of Man
Star: Jason Statham, Holt McCallany, Josh Hartnett, Rocci Williams
Summary: The plot follows H, a cold and mysterious character working at a cash truck company responsible for moving hundreds of millions of dollars around Los Angeles each week.

Name: Last Night in Soho
Star: Thomasin McKenzie, Anya Taylor-Joy, Matt Smith, Diana Rigg
Summary: An aspiring fashion designer is mysteriously able to enter the 1960s where she encounters a dazzling wannabe singer. But the glamour is not all it appears to be and the dreams of the past start to crack and splinter into something darker.

Name: Stranger Things
Star: Millie Bobby Brown, Finn Wolfhard, Winona Ryder, David Harbour
Summary: When a young boy disappears, his mother, a police chief and his friends must confront terrifying supernatural forces in order to get him back.

Name: A Christmas Carol
Star: Jim Carrey, Gary Oldman, Colin Firth, Steve Valentine
Summary: An animated retelling of Charles Dickens' classic novel about a Victorian-era miser taken on a journey of self-redemption, courtesy of several mysterious Christmas apparitions.

Name: Criminal Minds
Star: Matthew Gray Gubler, Kirsten Vangsness, A.J. Cook, Joe Mantegna
Summary: The cases of the F.B.I. Behavioral Analysis Unit (B.A.U.), an elite group of profilers who analyze the nation's most dangerous serial killers and individual heinous crimes in an effort to anticipate their next moves before they strike again.

Name: American Horror Story
Star: Lady Gaga, Kathy Bates, Angela Bassett, Sarah Paulson
Summary: An anthology series centering on different characters and locations, including a house with a murderous past, an insane asylum, a witch coven, a freak show circus, a haunted hotel, a possessed farmhouse, a cult, the apocalypse, a slasher summer camp, and a bleak beach town and desert valley.

Name: Law & Order: Special Victims Unit
Star: Mariska Hargitay, Christopher Meloni, Ice-T, Dann Florek
Summary: This series follows the Special Victims Unit, a specially trained squad of detectives in the N.Y.P.D., who investigate sexually related crimes.

Name: Morbius
Star: Michael Keaton, Jared Leto, Adria Arjona, Jared Harris
Summary: Biochemist Michael Morbius tries to cure himself of a rare blood disease, but he inadvertently infects himself with a form of vampirism instead.

Name: The Silent Sea
Star: Bae Doona, Gong Yoo, Joon Lee, Feodor Chin
Summary: During a perilous 24-hour mission on the moon, space explorers try to retrieve samples from an abandoned research facility steeped in classified secrets.

Name: Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba
Star: Natsuki Hanae, Zach Aguilar, Hiro Shimono, Yoshitsugu Matsuoka
Summary: A family is attacked by demons and only two members survive - Tanjiro and his sister Nezuko, who is turning into a demon slowly. Tanjiro sets out to become a demon slayer to avenge his family and cure his sister.

Name: Black Mirror
Star: Daniel Lapaine, Hannah John-Kamen, Michaela Coel, Beatrice Robertson-Jones
Summary: An anthology series exploring a twisted, high-tech multiverse where humanity's greatest innovations and darkest instincts collide.

Name: The Novice
Star: Isabelle Fuhrman, Amy Forsyth, Dilone, Jonathan Cherry
Summary: A college freshman joins her university's rowing team and undertakes an obsessive physical and psychological journey to make it to the top varsity boat, no matter the cost.

Name: The Dark Knight
Star: Christian Bale, Heath Ledger, Aaron Eckhart, Michael Caine
Summary: When the menace known as the Joker wreaks havoc and chaos on the people of Gotham, Batman must accept one of the greatest psychological and physical tests of his ability to fight injustice.

Name: True Story
Star: Kevin Hart, Wesley Snipes, William Catlett, Paul Adelstein
Summary: A tour stop in Kid's hometown of Philadelphia becomes a matter of life and death for one of the world's most famous comedians.

Name: Aranyak
Star: Parambrata Chattopadhyay, Ashutosh Rana, Raveena Tandon, Taneesha Joshi
Summary: Political ploys, personal agendas and a beastly myth all surface as two mismatched hill station cops navigate a web of suspects after a puzzling murder.

Name: Ozark
Star: Jason Bateman, Laura Linney, Sofia Hublitz, Skylar Gaertner
Summary: A financial advisor drags his family from Chicago to the Missouri Ozarks, where he must launder money to appease a drug boss.

Name: Kingsman: The Secret Service
Star: Colin Firth, Taron Egerton, Samuel L. Jackson, Michael Caine
Summary: A spy organisation recruits a promising street kid into the agency's training program, while a global threat emerges from a twisted tech genius.

Name: Only Murders in the Building
Star: Steve Martin, Martin Short, Selena Gomez, Aaron Dominguez
Summary: Three strangers who share an obsession with true crime suddenly find themselves caught up in one.

Name: The Wire
Star: Dominic West, Lance Reddick, Sonja Sohn, Wendell Pierce
Summary: The Baltimore drug scene, as seen through the eyes of drug dealers and law enforcement.

Name: Encounter
Star: Riz Ahmed, Octavia Spencer, Lucian-River Chauhan, Aditya Geddada
Summary: Two brothers embark on a journey with their father, who is trying to protect them from an alien threat.

Name: The Vampire Diaries
Star: Nina Dobrev, Paul Wesley, Ian Somerhalder, Kat Graham
Summary: The lives, loves, dangers and disasters in the town, Mystic Falls, Virginia. Creatures of unspeakable horror lurk beneath this town as a teenage girl is suddenly torn between two vampire brothers.

Name: Fargo
Star: Billy Bob Thornton, Martin Freeman, Allison Tolman, Colin Hanks
Summary: Various chronicles of deception, intrigue and murder in and around frozen Minnesota. Yet all of these tales mysteriously lead back one way or another to Fargo, North Dakota.

Name: Die Hard 2
Star: Bruce Willis, William Atherton, Bonnie Bedelia, Reginald VelJohnson
Summary: John McClane attempts to avert disaster as rogue military operatives seize control of Dulles International Airport in Washington, D.C.
